Properties
One interesting property of 
  
    
      
        
          
            2
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\sqrt {2}}}
   is

  
    
      
        
         
        
          
            1
            
              
                
                  2
                
              
              −
              1
            
          
        
        =
        
          
            2
          
        
        +
        1
      
    
    {\displaystyle \!\ {1 \over {{\sqrt {2}}-1}}={\sqrt {2}}+1}
  since

  
    
      
        
          (
          
            
              
